Kea Lease DNS Sync

Synchronizes Kea DHCP leases and static reservations to Unbound DNS.
Registers each host under a direct-access domain (real IP) and one or
more proxy domains (reverse proxy IP), with automatic PTR records.

Includes a dashboard widget with table and network map views.

WWW: https://github.com/c0de-ch/opnsense-plugin-c0de-kimlab
